Timing adjusted according to gun trigger (ref. event #16 with 10ms delay)
timing obeserved and optimized with FC-signal and RF-signal on scope
=> trigger LLRF #1,2,3 delay=9997.5us
=> trigger MOD #1,2,3 delay=9995.5us
=> trigger RF det. delay=9995.5us

There is water on the floor by the 2 electrical panels by the bathroom. There is no water on the panels. According to Geroge Ganetis:\n The front of one of the panels is open because of a lock. \nThe water on the floor is from a hydrostatic test on the water system and this water is from a valve. Nobody had cleaned it up. There is no danger unless we are working there and we are not.
